      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it just feels like i'm just taking up space now. they're so busy and young and they have so much to do. instead of them spending their weekends worrying about my appointments or my health, they could just... be free. i keep thinking about how much easier everything would be for everyone if i just wasn't here to be a problem anymore. isn't there some kind of peace in just letting go so they can finally live their lives?",
